name: Norwegian 787-8 "Dreamliner" EI-LNB First Flight takeoff at Paine Field
description:
Hello fellow youtubers, I'm back!
Sorry for the lack of activity this past week. I was on vacation, and I went to Seattle! I have about 4 hours of footage from Seattle-Tacoma International Airport, Boeing Field, and Paine Field, although most of the footage is from Paine. I tried a bit of spotting at Sea-Tac, but that didn't go so well, as I was having difficulty finding a good spot. I have much more coming, so stay tuned ;)

Enjoy this footage of a Norwegian Boeing 787-8 Dreamliner departing Paine Field on its maiden flight!

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
